---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Graphic from "../../components/Graphic.astro";
---

<Layout title="SME Scaling | Hire Desk Case Study">
  <article class="case-study-page">
    <div class="case-study-hero" style="--accent: #54c6d7;">
      <div class="absolute-graphic">
        <Graphic opacity={0.08} size={600} themeColor="#54c6d7" />
      </div>
      <div class="container--narrow">
        <div class="hero-top reveal">
          <span class="category">SME Scaling</span>
          <h1 class="hero-title">Bringing structure and consistency to a scaling business</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">When growth starts to outpace your systems</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="case-study-content">
      <div class="container--narrow">
        <div class="content-section reveal">
          <div class="label-box">
             <span class="label-text">The Client</span>
             <svg class="label-scribble" viewBox="0 0 100 20"><path d="M5 15 Q50 20 95 15" stroke="#54c6d7" stroke-width="2" fill="none"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="meta-info">Growing SME</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section reveal">
          <h2>The Challenge</h2>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p>
              As the business grew, internal processes struggled to keep up. Key tasks such as admin, reporting and customer communication were being handled inconsistently, often by different people, leading to inefficiencies and delays.
            </p>
            <p>
              The leadership team was spending increasing amounts of time managing operational detail instead of focusing on growth.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-visual reveal">
           <Graphic opacity={0.15} size={400} themeColor="#54c6d7" />
        </div>

        <div class="reality-box reveal">
          <h3>Our Approach</h3>
          <p>Hire Desk worked closely with the business to understand how work was being managed day-to-day. We introduced structured support across:</p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Back-office administration</li>
            <li>CRM and data management</li>
            <li>Customer communication support</li>
            <li>Reporting and workflow organisation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="outcome-box reveal">
          <h2>The Outcome</h2>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p>
              The business became more organised, with clearer processes and more consistent delivery across key areas. The leadership team was able to step away from day-to-day coordination and refocus on growing the business.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="results-grid">
             <div class="result-item">
                <span class="val">Insight</span>
                <p>Improved operational consistency</p>
             </div>
             <div class="result-item">
                <span class="val">Relief</span>
                <p>Reduced pressure on internal team</p>
             </div>
             <div class="result-item">
                <span class="val">Growth</span>
                <p>More time for leadership to focus on growth</p>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="page-footer-nav reveal">
          <a href="/get-started" class="btn btn-black">Accelerate Your Growth</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .case-study-hero {
    background-color: #f0fbff;
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .absolute-graphic {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .approach-visual {
    position: absolute;
    right: -100px;
    top: 40%;
    opacity: 0.4;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container--narrow {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .category {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #000;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #555;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .case-study-content {
    padding: 80px 0 120px;
    background-color: #fff;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .label-box {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .label-text {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #999;
  }

  .label-scribble {
    width: 100%;
    height: 12px;
    margin-top: -4px;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .meta-info {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .text-block p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reality-box {
    background-color: rgba(84, 198, 215, 0.05);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(84, 198, 215, 0.1);
  }

  .reality-box h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .check-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .check-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #000;
  }

  .check-list li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: -2px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: #54c6d7;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .result-item {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .result-item .val {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #54c6d7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .result-item p {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .page-footer-nav {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .check-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .results-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .reality-box { padding: 2rem; }
    .approach-visual { display: none; }
  }
</style>
